1.0.0.description:
1 - Social Share extension allows the user to add and manage multiple social share links from admin panel. &#xD;
2 - Here user can add social icons images according to site theme. &#xD;
3 - Enable or Disable any respective share link or whole extension. &#xD;
4 - Users have option to show a group of all the social share link's icon on left or right section of the screen. &#xD;
5 - User can manage the position of any respective share link's icon on front-end.&#xD;
